headline: ROLLINS, INC. SCHEDULES DATE FOR RELEASE OF SECOND QUARTER 2025 FINANCIAL RESULTS
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL) ("Rollins" or the "Company"), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, today announced that it will release its second quarter results for the period ended June 30, 2025, after the market closes on Wednesday, July 23, 2025. In conjunction with its release, the Company will host a conference call to review the Company's financial and operating results before the market opens on Thursday, July 24, 2025, at 8:30 a.m. Eastern Time.
